Berkshire Hathaway HomeServices Starck Real Estate

data.description: Welcome to this beautifully updated and well maintained home! Located in Silver Lakes, this 4 bed/3 bath home is gleaming from top to bottom with an open living space flowing into the large kitchen. The kitchen features modern white cabinets, granite countertops and all stainless steel appliances, with the family room just steps off of the kitchen with a large brick fireplace. Generously sized bedrooms and all 3 full bathrooms have been recently updated. This home has a full finished basement with a full laundry/utility room. The backyard is fully fenced in with a large deck and above-ground pool that is perfect for entertaining. This home conveniently backs up to Silver Lakes Golf Course and is in close proximity to shopping centers, restaurants, and parks.
